subNodes.conversationText: root
What do we have here?  You do not appear to be mercenaries of Jadissan.
Jadissan?
I take it you have no knowledge of the witch?
You mean Zorn's witch?
Yes, but I know nothing of the rumored return of Zorn.
Do you know much about the witch, Jadissan?
Unfortunately, yes.  It is because of her that I left my home in the volcano mountains.
It appears that we have a common enemy.  May we ask you a few questions about her?
I suppose...what would you like to know?
Do you know of the witch's origin?
Not all of it.  She came from another world of which I am not familiar.
She did not come alone.  She was in pursuit of the Lizard Queen who she chased into a cave.
That cave was a path from her world to ours.  They both arrived here at slightly different times.
The Lizard Queen was able to escape.
Jadissan had to relearn her powers as her knowledge from her world did not work here.
Interesting...may we ask another question?
What rumors have you heard about Zorn's return?
Not many.  I have not seen him with my own eyes so I am skeptical.
The rumors could have originated from Jadissan herself.
One rumor was that Zorn called her into this world and maybe she is using that story to place herself in power.
I have overheard some swear that they have seen Zorn.
But again, I am skeptical since it was Elos, curse his name, that banished Zorn forever.
Interesting...may we ask another question?
What do you know about this area?
Not too far to the North is the Zornian Castle.
This forest was fairly calm, but since Jadissan arrived it has become fairly active again.
Zornian soldiers regularly patrol the area.
It works out great for me as it has created a never ending supply of fresh blood.
At the end of the canyon path is the entrance to the caves that eventually lead to the castle.
Thanks...may we ask another question?
We should probably get going.
If you meet Jadissan, give her my regards.
We shall...farewell.
I am really sorry that you lost your home, but I have no use for evil spider stories.
I am not looking for sympathy or company, but fresh blood sounds good.
We shall see...|***ga_faction_join-->String::Sulob    String::$HOSTILE    |
We meet again strangers...I'd like to chat, but I am a little busy at the moment.
